### Back-end: 

- Necessita do Maven 3 e do Java 17
- mvn spring-boot:run

- URL: https://localhost:8080

### Front-end:
- URL: https://orcamento-publico.vercel.app

- Acessar a pasta frontend pelo CMD e digitar "npm run dev"
